import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { BookingRm } from '../api/models'; import { BookingService } from './../api/services/booking.service'; import { AuthService } from './../auth/auth.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-my-bookings', templateUrl: './my-bookings.component.html', styleUrls: ['./my-bookings.component.css'] }) export class MyBookingsComponent implements OnInit { bookings!: BookingRm[]; constructor(private bookingService: BookingService, private authService: AuthService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.bookingService.listBooking({ email: this.authService.currentUser?.email?? '' }) .subscribe(result => this.bookings = result); } }
